Description:
  TheCommentsBase: generators will copy files to install TheComments 3.0 into your App

  Usage: [bundle exec] rails g the_comments_base OPTION_NAME
  Usage: [bundle exec] rails g the_comments_base:views OPTION_NAME

# This text:
  > rails g the_comments_base --help

# Main generators:
  > rails g the_comments_base install

  This will create:
    app/models/comment.rb
    app/controllers/comments_controller.rb
    config/initializers/the_comments_base.rb

# Model generators:
  > rails g the_comments_base models

  This will generate:
    app/models/comment.rb

# Controller generators:
  > rails g the_comments_base controllers

  This will create:
    app/controllers/comments_controller.rb

# Config generators:
  > rails g the_comments_base config

  This will generate:
    config/initializers/the_comments_base.rb

# Locales generators:
  > rails g the_comments_base locales

  This will generate:
    config/locales/en.the_comments_base.yml
    config/locales/ru.the_comments_base.yml

# All generators:
  > rails g the_comments_base all

  This will create:
    app/models/comment.rb
    app/controllers/comments_controller.rb
    config/initializers/the_comments_base.rb
    config/locales/en.the_comments_base.yml
    config/locales/ru.the_comments_base.yml

# View Generators:
  > rails g the_comments_base:views js
  > rails g the_comments_base:views css
  > rails g the_comments_base:views assets
  > rails g the_comments_base:views helper
  > rails g the_comments_base:views views

# Migrations:
  > rake the_comments_base_engine:install:migrations
